===If the player has a max cape in their inventory===
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* {{tbox|The man glances at you and grunts something unintelligible.}}
* {{topt|Who are you?}}
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|What do you have in your sack?}}
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|Can I sell my max cape back to you?}}
** '''Mac:''' Yip. Show me the goods. I pay 80%.
** {{tselect|Sell your [max cape variant] and hood back?}}
** {{topt|Yes - receive 1,900,800gp.}}
*** {{tcond|If the player only has the cape in their inventory:}}
**** {{tact|You sell your cape back to Mac.}}
**** {{tact|end}}
*** {{tcond|If the player has the matching hood in their inventory:}}
**** {{tact|You sell your cape and hood back to Mac.}}
**** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No, I've changed my mind.}}
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Can I have another hood for my cape?}}
** {{tcond|If the player does not have any free inventory space:}}
*** '''Mac:''' Nah. Need more space.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|If the player has at least one free inventory space:}}
*** '''Mac:''' Yip. No cost. What cape do you want a hood for?
*** {{tact|Interface opens showing which max hood variant the player wants to claim}}
*** {{tcond|If the player selects a max hood variant that they do not have the max cape variant for:}}
**** '''Mac:''' You don't have that cape. Choose another.
*** {{tcond|If the player selects a max hood variant that they have the max cape variant for:}}
**** {{tbox|Mac hands you another hood for your cape.}}
**** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Bye.}}
** {{tact|above}}

