===Using any max hood variant on Mac===
* '''Mac:''' Show cape.
* {{tact|end}}

===Using any max cape variant on Mac===
* {{tselect|Sell your [max cape variant] and hood back?}}
* {{topt|Yes - receive 1,900,800gp.}}
** {{tcond|If the player only has the cape in their inventory:}}
*** {{tact|You sell your cape back to Mac.}}
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|If the player has the matching hood in their inventory:}}
*** {{tact|You sell your cape and hood back to Mac.}}
*** {{tact|end}}

===Using any other item on Mac===
* '''Mac:''' That's XP waste.
* {{tact|end}}
